                <h1>Senior Emma Wright reflects on her Appalachian Trail solo hike </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/490d71bd-da6c-478b-8855-3df7d6b69a11.sized-1000x1000.png?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Senior&#x20;Emma&#x20;Wright&#x20;hiked&#x20;from&#x20;Georgia&#x20;to&#x20;Maine&#x20;this&#x20;year&#x20;along&#x20;the&#x20;Appalachian&#x20;Trail.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Senior Emma Wright hiked from Georgia to Maine this year along the Appalachian Trail.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/rob-palmisano">Rob Palmisano</a>
                                    
